title: Hour 1: Believe in the Browns?
description:
Stephen A., Marcus Spears, Ryan Clark, Adrian Wojnarowski and Jay Williams discuss Ime Udoka's year long suspension, who will be 0-3 after week 3 of the NFL season and is it time to start Kenny Pickett?
